IONode.Description: Performs specific I/O operations on embedded targets. You must select the I/O items you want to use by right-clicking the Elemental I/O Node on the block diagram and selecting Select Elemental I/O from the shortcut menu. The Select Elemental I/O submenu displays the Elemental I/O items that appear in the Project Explorer window below the same embedded target as the embedded VI you are currently editing.

Property.Description: Gets or sets one or more properties on an I/O item under an embedded target in the Project Explorer window. The I/O resources available and the associated properties vary by embedded target.
